@node Main "MySquare - Documentation"

                             'MySquare' 1.21

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  MySquare is a Workbench @{" game " link play} based on a popular mathematical
game in which you place a range of numbers in a grid. The @{" goal " link play} is
to place the numbers in such a way that their sum will be the same
everywhere (that is: horizontally, vertically and diagonally).

  Here's an example of a 3x3 grid:

                        @{" 6 " link play}@{" 1 " link play}@{" 8 " link play}
                        @{" 7 " link play}@{" 5 " link play}@{" 3 " link play}
                        @{" 2 " link play}@{" 9 " link play}@{" 4 " link play}

  In this example, the sums on every row, column and diagonal are
equal to 15.

  Have fun!

