@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "MySquare" where you want on
your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or Libraries
are needed.

                             How to play?

  You move a number in the grid on the left by clicking on it with the mouse
pointer and you click on the grid at right, where you want to place that
number. If the space is already occupied by a number, your choosen number
will take its place and the previous one will return to the grid on the
left. You can also move a number located in the grid at right to another
(empty or occupied) space in the same grid.

  The sums of each rows, columns and diagonals are indicated by the arrows
at the right and bottom of the grid. When the sum of the numbers equals
the 'fixed total' of that particular grid (the total you want to get),
its color will change to white.

  Continue to move the numbers, until all the sums are all equal to that
total (all the sums are in white).

  Have fun!

